{"id":2976,"date":"2025-06-05T09:44:31","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T02:44:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2976"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:18:54","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:18:54","slug":"da-mun-nen-an-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/da-mun-nen-an-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Da m\u1ee5n n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec v\u00e0 ki\u00eang \u0103n g\u00ec? Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00ean tr\u00e1nh khi b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n!"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>Da m\u1ee5n n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u1ec3 nhanh h\u1ebft m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong? N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eed \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1ch b\u00f4i ngo\u00e0i da nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee5n v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng thuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3m, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng. Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u1ee3i \u00fd \u0103n g\u00ec h\u1ebft m\u1ee5n, da m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1eb9o dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb g\u1ed1c!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-mun-nen-an-gi-nhung-thuc-pham-vang-giup-cai-thien-da-mun\"><\/span><b>Da m\u1ee5n n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec? Nh\u1eefng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0ng gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da m\u1ee5n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c tr\u00e1nh xa nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00f9i m\u1ee5n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u GSC khuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u00e0n da t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3795\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3795\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3795\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-1.webp\" alt=\"Da m\u1ee5n n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3795\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Da m\u1ee5n n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhom-thuc-pham-giau-chat-chong-oxy-hoa-%e2%80%93-bao-ve-da-khoi-goc-tu-do\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u00f3m th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a &#8211; B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a gi\u00fap trung h\u00f2a c\u00e1c g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do. Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng vi\u00eam. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u1ee3i \u00fd bao g\u1ed3m tr\u00e0 xanh, h\u1ea1t macca, s\u00f4 c\u00f4 la \u0111en, c\u00e0 chua, b\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i xanh, vi\u1ec7t qu\u1ea5t, d\u00e2u t\u00e2y, kiwi\u2026 Vi\u1ec7c th\u00eam ch\u00fang v\u00e0o b\u1eefa \u0103n h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"omega-3-%e2%80%93-chat-khang-viem-tu-nhien-cho-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Omega-3 &#8211; Ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cho da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Omega-3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu c\u00e1c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean da. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u Omega-3 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1 h\u1ed3i, c\u00e1 ng\u1eeb, c\u00e1 thu, h\u1ea1t lanh, qu\u1ea3 \u00f3c ch\u00f3\u2026 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da b\u1edbt m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ee5n t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thuc-pham-giau-probiotics-%e2%80%93-can-bang-he-vi-sinh-duong-ruot\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u Probiotics &#8211; C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u1ec7 vi sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ru\u1ed9t<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Probiotics kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u1ec7 vi sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ru\u1ed9t, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ru\u1ed9t kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o th\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ee5n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung probiotics qua s\u1eefa chua, d\u01b0a mu\u1ed1i, kefir, s\u00fap miso v\u00e0 tr\u00e0 kombucha.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3796\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3796\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3796\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-2-3.webp\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u Probiotics\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-2-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-2-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-2-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-2-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3796\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u Probiotics<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phytoestrogen-%e2%80%93-can-bang-noi-tiet-to\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Phytoestrogen &#8211; C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Phytoestrogen l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng hormone, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ee5n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam tr\u00ean da. C\u00e1c th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u phytoestrogen g\u1ed3m b\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i xanh, c\u00e0 r\u1ed1t, c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3 m\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 d\u00e2u t\u00e2y, vi\u1ec7t qu\u1ea5t, nho, s\u01a1 ri\u2026 B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vitamin-e-%e2%80%93-duong-chat-phuc-hoi-va-tai-tao-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin E &#8211; D\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0Vitamin E \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a m\u1ea1nh. Gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch, ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u vitamin E nh\u01b0 h\u1ea1t b\u00ed ng\u00f4, h\u1ea1t h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1ea1t th\u00f4ng, qu\u1ea3 b\u01a1, h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap da th\u00eam m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thuc-pham-giau-kem-%e2%80%93-tang-cuong-suc-de-khang-cho-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u k\u1ebdm &#8211; T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng cho da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3797\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3797\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3797\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-3-3.webp\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u k\u1ebdm\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-3-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-3-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-3-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-3-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3797\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u k\u1ebdm<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebdm \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch, ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 ch\u1eefa l\u00e0nh c\u00e1c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da do m\u1ee5n. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u k\u1ebdm nh\u01b0 h\u00e0u, s\u00f2, t\u00f4m h\u00f9m, \u0111\u1eadu H\u00e0 Lan, \u0111\u1eadu l\u0103ng, h\u1ea1t h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u01b0\u01a1ng, rong bi\u1ec3n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u00e0n da nhanh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-mun-khong-nen-an-gi-cac-thuc-phan-nen-tranh-khi-bi-mun\"><\/span><b>Da m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec? C\u00e1c th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9n n\u00ean tr\u00e1nh khi b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh, hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea7n ki\u00eang khem c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. V\u1eady da m\u1ee5n n\u00ean tr\u00e1nh \u0103n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m, \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ea7u? D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00f3m th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m b\u1ea1n n\u00ean c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3798\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3798\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3798\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-4-3.webp\" alt=\"Da m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-4-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-4-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-4-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-4-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3798\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Da m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duong-%e2%80%93-%e2%80%98ke-thu-am-tham-cua-lan-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng &#8211; &#8216;K\u1ebb th\u00f9&#8217; \u00e2m th\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3 ng\u1ecdt c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng nhanh l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng trong m\u00e1u, k\u00edch th\u00edch tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ee5y s\u1ea3n sinh insulin. N\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 insulin cao s\u1ebd th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, khi\u1ebfn da ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho m\u1ee5n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n nh\u01b0 b\u00e1nh ng\u1ecdt, k\u1eb9o, socola, n\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1ecdt c\u00f3 ga\u2026 Thay v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, h\u00e3y chuy\u1ec3n sang c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1eadt m\u00eda, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ed1t n\u1ed1t ho\u1eb7c c\u1ecf ng\u1ecdt stevia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 \u1edf m\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"sua-bo-va-cac-che-pham-tu-sua-con-dao-hai-luoi-cho-lan-da-mun\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa b\u00f2 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb s\u1eefa- Con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i cho l\u00e0n da m\u1ee5n<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa b\u00f2, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 s\u1eefa t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng con b\u00f2 \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n mang thai c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u hormone t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 androgen. Nh\u1eefng hormone n\u00e0y l\u00e0m t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc, g\u00e2y ra m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3799\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3799\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3799\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-5-3.webp\" alt=\"S\u1eefa b\u00f2 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb s\u1eefa\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-5-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-5-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-5-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-5-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3799\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1eefa b\u00f2 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb s\u1eefa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1eefa kh\u1ecfi th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng n\u00ean ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u00eau th\u1ee5. C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean u\u1ed1ng kho\u1ea3ng 2\u20136 ly s\u1eefa\/tu\u1ea7n v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb s\u1eefa nh\u01b0 ph\u00f4 mai, s\u1eefa \u0111\u1eb7c, b\u01a1\u2026 \u0110\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt nh\u01b0 s\u1eefa h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n, s\u1eefa y\u1ebfn m\u1ea1ch ho\u1eb7c s\u1eefa \u0111\u1eadu n\u00e0nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thuc-pham-cay-nong-%e2%80%98cham-ngoi-cho-mun-viem-bung-phat\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m cay n\u00f3ng- &#8216;Ch\u00e2m ng\u00f2i&#8217; cho m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ee9c \u0103n cay n\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 m\u00ec cay, \u1edbt, ti\u00eau, m\u00f9 t\u1ea1t\u2026 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u00e3n m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u, k\u00edch th\u00edch tuy\u1ebfn m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ea7u h\u01a1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 vi khu\u1ea9n P.acnes ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, l\u00e0m tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng th\u00eam t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ee5n, t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n n\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u00e1c m\u00f3n cay n\u00f3ng. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed5 sung th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 t\u00ednh m\u00e1t nh\u01b0 rau xanh, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y, tr\u00e0 th\u1ea3o m\u1ed9c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap thanh l\u1ecdc c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"do-an-nhanh-dong-hop-tac-nhan-roi-loan-noi-tiet\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh, \u0111\u00f3ng h\u1ed9p- T\u00e1c nh\u00e2n r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c m\u00f3n \u0103n nhanh nh\u01b0 g\u00e0 r\u00e1n, khoai t\u00e2y chi\u00ean, pizza, x\u00fac x\u00edch\u2026 th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5t b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, mu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o b\u00e3o h\u00f2a. Nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho da m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0m t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3800\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3800\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3800\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-6.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh, \u0111\u00f3ng h\u1ed9p\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-6.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-6-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-6-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-6-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3800\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh, \u0111\u00f3ng h\u1ed9p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay v\u00ec \u0103n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u00f3ng h\u1ed9p ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh, b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y t\u1ef1 n\u1ea5u c\u00e1c m\u00f3n \u0103n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0, \u01b0u ti\u00ean th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eeba b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, v\u1eeba gi\u00fap da th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5-quy-tac-%e2%80%98vang-giup-xay-dung-che-do-an-uong-khoa-hoc-cho-da-mun\"><\/span><b>5 Quy t\u1eafc &#8216;v\u00e0ng&#8217; gi\u00fap x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc cho da m\u1ee5n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 quy t\u1eafc &#8216;v\u00e0ng&#8217; b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm v\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho l\u00e0n da m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3801\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3801\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3801\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-7.webp\" alt=\"5 Quy t\u1eafc 'v\u00e0ng' gi\u00fap x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-7.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-7-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-7-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-7-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3801\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">5 Quy t\u1eafc &#8216;v\u00e0ng&#8217; gi\u00fap x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chon-loc-thuc-pham-co-loi-va-tranh-xa-thuc-pham-gay-mun\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh xa th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n. Theo c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u, th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng huy\u1ebft th\u1ea5p (nh\u01b0 rau xanh, c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eadu, h\u1ea1t, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u1ecdt) v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1, vitamin, kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0n da t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng huy\u1ebft cao (nh\u01b0 b\u00e1nh ng\u1ecdt, n\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1ecdt c\u00f3 ga, \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n sinh IGF-1 (Insulin-like Growth Factor-1). Hormone n\u00e0y l\u00e0m t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t Androgen \u2014 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u00edt t\u1eafc v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duy-tri-su-can-bang-giua-cac-nhom-chat\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m ch\u1ea5t<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o hay tinh b\u1ed9t. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1eefa \u0103n cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 4 nh\u00f3m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu: Ch\u1ea5t b\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh, ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m, vitamin v\u00e0 kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t. S\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch cho l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"xay-dung-thoi-quen-an-uong-lanh-manh-va-co-ke-hoach\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u00f3i quen \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3756\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3756\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3756\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3756\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i &#8220;\u0103n g\u00ec c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&#8221;. H\u00e3y l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n cho t\u1eebng tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh, tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng b\u1eefa \u0103n v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u01b0u ti\u00ean d\u00f9ng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m theo m\u00f9a kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb t\u01b0\u01a1i ngon nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nguy c\u01a1 n\u1ea1p v\u00e0o c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n ho\u1eb7c h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c h\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uu-tien-bua-an-tu-nau-han-che-thuc-pham-che-bien-san\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu ti\u00ean b\u1eefa \u0103n t\u1ef1 n\u1ea5u, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn s\u1eb5n<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ee9c \u0103n nhanh hay \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn s\u1eb5n th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u m\u1ee1, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tinh luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 gia v\u1ecb, d\u1ec5 l\u00e0m tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam m\u1ee5n. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c m\u00f3n \u0103n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0, \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1ch ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 h\u1ea5p, lu\u1ed9c, n\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 t\u00edch t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1 trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3802\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3802\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3802\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-8.webp\" alt=\"\u01afu ti\u00ean b\u1eefa \u0103n t\u1ef1 n\u1ea5u, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn s\u1eb5n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-8.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-8-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-8-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/19-8-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3802\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u01afu ti\u00ean b\u1eefa \u0103n t\u1ef1 n\u1ea5u, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn s\u1eb5n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bo-sung-du-nuoc-moi-ngay\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c thanh l\u1ecdc c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cho da. Khi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc, tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn s\u1ebd ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t, khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb nh\u1eddn r\u00edt v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o u\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 2 &#8211; 2.5 l\u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc\/ng\u00e0y, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u00eam tr\u00e0 th\u1ea3o m\u1ed9c, n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e9p rau c\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Da m\u1ee5n n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">? Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 GSC chia s\u1ebb \u1edf tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0ng hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 \u201cm\u1ee5n\u201d v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean truy c\u1eadp website c\u1ee7a gsc vi\u1ec7t nam m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb9o h\u1eefu \u00edch kh\u00e1c nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u1ee3i \u00fd \u0103n g\u00ec h\u1ebft m\u1ee5n, da m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0103n g\u00ec v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1eb9o dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb g\u1ed1c!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3794,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2976","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2976","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2976"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2976\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3974,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2976\/revisions\/3974"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3794"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2976"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2976"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2976"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}